{"tid":1341365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府強烈譴責上環與元朗暴力行為","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:26:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46bcebed76155d0b42a19b0bc12c8f152a013b7b","tid":1341365,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469604-20190722.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469604-20190722.htm&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRf2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=ed405fac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469604-20190722.htm&h=45dc6442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469604-20190722.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府強烈譴責上環與元朗暴力行為 會嚴正追究<br />\n2019-07-22 HKT 00:24<br />\n<br />\n政府深夜發聲明，一併就上環及元朗發生的暴力行為作出回應，並予以強烈譴責，表明會嚴正追究。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，繼早前衝擊中聯辦大樓後，再有激進示威者無視警方多次警告，在上環一向警方發動連番暴力襲擊，包括投擲汽油彈、縱火、擲磚，並堵塞主要幹道，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又說，與此同時，在元朗有人聚眾於港鐵車站月台及車廂內襲擊乘客，引發衝突，導致有人受傷，重申香港作為法治社會，完全不能容忍任何暴力行為。"},{"pid":"935316d1f6150ba939538ddb0328eafce7f8fa32","tid":1341365,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"扮哂野? &nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ba23cadf974290e08bcd5160673ec1d3e34746","tid":1341365,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"收皮啦扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc3c8472b507c7aa156d9f706db9e0c426e8112","tid":1341365,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:43:40.000Z","msg":"香港警隊已徹底喪失維持治安能力，民眾要自保必須自組民兵團。"},{"pid":"70c771395658c8d0de6b5a8701501c76df92120f","tid":1341365,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:48:58.000